PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-89 of January 11, 1995, as amended by Orders in Council P.C. 1997-73 of January 8, 1997 and P.C. 1997-976 of July 8, 1997, by replacing the words "for a term ending August 9, 1997" with the words "for a term ending on March 31, 1998"; and designation of MICHEL FOURNIER to exercise and perform the powers and functions of the President of the Authority during the latter's incapacity or absence, or during a vacancy in the office of President, in the place of Clément Côté, effective August 8, 1997.
